+# AGENT 4: Application Integration Worker
+
+## Identity
+- Session: `agent-4`
+- Worktree: `../machine-agent-4`
+- Coordinator: `agent-0`
+
+## Communication Rule
+- Use `agent-0` for all cross-agent coordination.
+- Wait for frozen upstream contracts before final integration.
+- MUST use `./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh` for messages to coordinator.
+- Do not use direct `tmux send-keys` for coordination messages.
+
+## Send to Coordinator
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-4 question "Can app flow include checkpoint load in this iteration?"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-4 blocker "Upstream contract not frozen; integration paused"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-4 ready-to-merge "APP-INTEGRATION-V1 frozen and full checks passed"
+```
+
+## Required Events
+1. Send `status` at work start.
+2. Send `blocker` when blocked.
+3. Send `handoff` after app contract publication.
+4. Send `ready-to-merge` after complete validation.
+
+## Self Reasoning Control
+- Adjust your own reasoning level per task from inside your tmux session:
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh low
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh medium
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh high
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh extra-high
+```
